<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Constant Creates — Daily Brief</title>
<link rel="icon" type="image/svg+xml" href="data:image/svg+xml,<svg xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg' viewBox='0 0 32 32'><rect width='32' height='32' rx='6' fill='%231a2428'/><text x='16' y='22' font-size='18' font-family='serif' font-weight='bold' fill='%23c8d9a0' text-anchor='middle'>CC</text></svg>">
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Poppins:wght@300;400;500;600;700&family=Playfair+Display:wght@400;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
*,*::before,*::after{box-sizing:border-box;margin:0;padding:0}
:root{
  --dark:#1a2428;
  --forest:#263633;
  --green:#4a6650;
  --sage:#c8d9a0;
  --cream:#f0edd8;
  --text:#e8e4d0;
  --muted:#8a9a88;
  --danger:#c0392b;
  --warn:#d47c0f;
  --info:#2980b9;
  --success:#27ae60;
  --card-bg:#1e2d2a;
  --border:#2e3f3c;
}
body{background:var(--dark);color:var(--text);font-family:'Poppins',sans-serif;font-size:14px;line-height:1.6;min-height:100vh}
#gate{position:fixed;inset:0;background:var(--dark);display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;z-index:9999;flex-direction:column;gap:20px}
#gate h1{font-family:'Playfair Display',serif;color:var(--sage);font-size:28px}
#gate p{color:var(--muted);font-size:13px}
#gate input{background:var(--forest);border:1px solid var(--border);color:var(--text);padding:12px 20px;border-radius:8px;font-size:15px;width:260px;text-align:center;outline:none}
#gate input:focus{border-color:var(--sage)}
#gate button{background:var(--green);color:var(--cream);border:none;padding:12px 32px;border-radius:8px;font-size:14px;font-family:'Poppins',sans-serif;font-weight:600;cursor:pointer;letter-spacing:.5px}
#gate button:hover{background:var(--sage);color:var(--dark)}
#gate .err{color:#e74c3c;font-size:12px;display:none}
#dashboard{display:none}
.wrap{max-width:1100px;margin:0 auto;padding:24px 20px}
header{display:flex;justify-content:space-between;align-items:center;margin-bottom:24px;padding-bottom:16px;border-bottom:1px solid var(--border)}
.logo{font-family:'Playfair Display',serif;font-size:20px;color:var(--sage);letter-spacing:.5px}
.datestamp{color:var(--muted);font-size:12px;text-align:right}
.hero{background:linear-gradient(135deg,var(--forest) 0%,#1e3028 100%);border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:12px;padding:24px 28px;margin-bottom:20px}
.hero h2{font-family:'Playfair Display',serif;font-size:22px;color:var(--cream);margin-bottom:6px}
.hero p{color:var(--muted);font-size:13px}
.alerts{display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:10px;margin-bottom:24px}
.alert{border-radius:8px;padding:12px 16px;font-size:13px;display:flex;align-items:flex-start;gap:10px;border-left:4px solid}
.alert-icon{font-size:16px;margin-top:1px;flex-shrink:0}
.alert-body strong{display:block;margin-bottom:2px;font-weight:600}
.alert-body span{opacity:.85}
.alert.success{background:rgba(39,174,96,.12);border-color:var(--success);color:#7fd8a0}
.alert.warn{background:rgba(212,124,15,.12);border-color:var(--warn);color:#e8a84e}
.alert.danger{background:rgba(192,57,43,.12);border-color:var(--danger);color:#e07070}
.alert.info{background:rgba(41,128,185,.12);border-color:var(--info);color:#72b8e0}
.section-title{font-family:'Playfair Display',serif;font-size:16px;color:var(--sage);margin-bottom:14px;padding-bottom:6px;border-bottom:1px solid var(--border)}
.grid-4{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(4,1fr);gap:14px;margin-bottom:24px}
.grid-2{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:14px;margin-bottom:24px}
.grid-3{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(3,1fr);gap:14px;margin-bottom:24px}
.card{background:var(--card-bg);border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:10px;padding:18px}
.metric{text-align:center}
.metric .val{font-family:'Playfair Display',serif;font-size:26px;color:var(--sage);font-weight:700;line-height:1}
.metric .lbl{color:var(--muted);font-size:11px;margin-top:4px;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:.5px}
.metric .sub{color:var(--text);font-size:11px;margin-top:4px}
.badge{display:inline-block;font-size:10px;font-weight:600;padding:2px 8px;border-radius:20px;letter-spacing:.4px;text-transform:uppercase}
.badge-green{background:rgba(74,102,80,.35);color:var(--sage)}
.badge-warn{background:rgba(212,124,15,.25);color:#e8a84e}
.badge-danger{background:rgba(192,57,43,.25);color:#e07070}
.badge-info{background:rgba(41,128,185,.25);color:#72b8e0}
.badge-muted{background:rgba(138,154,136,.15);color:var(--muted)}
.client-card{background:var(--card-bg);border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:10px;padding:16px;margin-bottom:12px}
.client-header{display:flex;justify-content:space-between;align-items:flex-start;margin-bottom:8px}
.client-name{font-weight:600;color:var(--cream);font-size:14px}
.client-biz{color:var(--muted);font-size:11px;margin-top:1px}
.client-detail{font-size:12px;color:var(--text);margin-bottom:4px}
.client-detail strong{color:var(--sage)}
.divider{border:none;border-top:1px solid var(--border);margin:20px 0}
.action-list{list-style:none;display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:8px}
.action-item{display:flex;align-items:flex-start;gap:12px;background:var(--card-bg);border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:8px;padding:12px 14px;cursor:pointer;transition:border-color .2s}
.action-item:hover{border-color:var(--sage)}
.action-item.done{opacity:.45}
.action-item.done .action-text{text-decoration:line-through}
.action-cb{width:18px;height:18px;border:2px solid var(--green);border-radius:4px;flex-shrink:0;margin-top:1px;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;color:var(--sage);font-size:12px}
.action-item.done .action-cb{background:var(--green)}
.action-num{font-family:'Playfair Display',serif;font-size:18px;color:var(--sage);font-weight:700;flex-shrink:0;width:24px}
.action-body{flex:1}
.action-text{font-weight:500;color:var(--cream);font-size:13px;display:block}
.action-meta{font-size:11px;color:var(--muted);margin-top:2px}
.email-row{display:flex;align-items:flex-start;gap:10px;padding:10px 0;border-bottom:1px solid var(--border)}
.email-row:last-child{border-bottom:none}
.email-icon{font-size:14px;margin-top:2px;flex-shrink:0}
.email-body{flex:1}
.email-from{font-weight:500;color:var(--cream);font-size:12px}
.email-subj{color:var(--text);font-size:12px}
.email-note{color:var(--muted);font-size:11px;margin-top:1px}
.checklist{display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:6px}
.check-row{display:flex;align-items:flex-start;gap:8px;font-size:12px}
.check-dot{width:8px;height:8px;border-radius:50%;flex-shrink:0;margin-top:4px}
.dot-danger{background:var(--danger)}
.dot-warn{background:var(--warn)}
.dot-ok{background:var(--success)}
.upcoming-list{display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:8px}
.upcoming-row{display:flex;gap:12px;align-items:flex-start;font-size:12px}
.upcoming-day{color:var(--sage);font-weight:600;width:80px;flex-shrink:0}
.upcoming-desc{color:var(--text)}
.sys-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(3,1fr);gap:10px;margin-bottom:24px}
.sys-item{background:var(--card-bg);border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:8px;padding:12px}
.sys-label{font-size:11px;color:var(--muted);text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:.4px}
.sys-val{font-size:13px;color:var(--cream);font-weight:500;margin-top:4px}
footer{text-align:center;color:var(--muted);font-size:11px;padding:20px 0;border-top:1px solid var(--border);margin-top:24px}
@media(max-width:700px){.grid-4,.grid-3{grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr}.grid-2{grid-template-columns:1fr}.sys-grid{grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr}}
@media(max-width:480px){.grid-4{grid-template-columns:1fr}}
</style>
</head>
<body>

<!-- PASSWORD GATE -->
<div id="gate">
  <h1>CC Daily Brief</h1>
  <p>Saturday, April 4, 2026</p>
  <input type="password" id="pw" placeholder="Enter password" onkeydown="if(event.key==='Enter')unlock()">
  <button onclick="unlock()">Unlock</button>
  <span class="err" id="err">Wrong password. Try again.</span>
</div>

<!-- DASHBOARD -->
<div id="dashboard">
<div class="wrap">

  <header>
    <div class="logo">Constant Creates</div>
    <div class="datestamp">
      <div style="font-weight:600;color:var(--cream)">Saturday, April 4, 2026</div>
      <div>Daily Brief · Generated 5:00 AM ET</div>
    </div>
  </header>

  <!-- HERO -->
  <div class="hero">
    <h2>It's the weekend, Faye 🎉&nbsp; The VMC site is live.</h2>
    <p>Big week. Lakewood Ranch Vet launched Friday. Derek is officially onboarded. Clay's ACH likely cleared overnight. You've got a clean Saturday to knock out quick wins before the week kicks off Monday.</p>
  </div>

  <!-- ALERTS -->
  <div class="alerts">
    <div class="alert success">
      <span class="alert-icon">✅</span>
      <div class="alert-body">
        <strong>VMC Website Live — lakewoodranchvet.com</strong>
        <span>Launched Friday, April 3. Verify it's rendering correctly on mobile + desktop. 5 critical items still on the post-launch checklist (see below).</span>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="alert warn">
      <span class="alert-icon">🏦</span>
      <div class="alert-body">
        <strong>Chase ACH — Likely Clay Griffin's $600 Retainer</strong>
        <span>ACH deposits typically process overnight. Clay's payment is due the 6th — check Chase now and manually mark his HoneyBook invoice paid if it cleared.</span>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="alert danger">
      <span class="alert-icon">📧</span>
      <div class="alert-body">
        <strong>Angela Jones Email Bounced — Wrong Address Used</strong>
        <span>Reply sent Apr 2 to angelajonesent@gmail.com — BOUNCED. Correct address is angela.jones013p@gmail.com. "A Clothing" logo inquiry at $1K budget. Resend today (no links — all info in body).</span>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="alert info">
      <span class="alert-icon">🔄</span>
      <div class="alert-body">
        <strong>Contra Pro Renews Monday, April 6 — Decide Today</strong>
        <span>Freelance contract tool renewing on Monday. If you're not actively using it, cancel before Monday to avoid the charge. Log in and decide now.</span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- REVENUE SNAPSHOT -->
  <div class="section-title">💰 Revenue Snapshot</div>
  <div class="grid-4" style="margin-bottom:24px">
    <div class="card metric">
      <div class="val">$3,200</div>
      <div class="lbl">Confirmed MRR</div>
      <div class="sub">Clay $600 + VMC $2,000 + Derek est. $600</div>
    </div>
    <div class="card metric">
      <div class="val" style="color:#e8a84e">$600</div>
      <div class="lbl">Clay ACH — Verify</div>
      <div class="sub">Due the 6th · Check Chase + HoneyBook</div>
    </div>
    <div class="card metric">
      <div class="val" style="color:#e8a84e">$300</div>
      <div class="lbl">Derek Deposit Pending</div>
      <div class="sub">50% of $600/mo · Zelle or Venmo</div>
    </div>
    <div class="card metric">
      <div class="val" style="color:#e07070">$1,800</div>
      <div class="lbl">Nancy Pipeline at Risk</div>
      <div class="sub">30 days no reply · Trinity UMC logo</div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="card" style="margin-bottom:24px;text-align:center;padding:14px">
    <span style="color:var(--muted);font-size:12px">Annual Goal Progress: </span>
    <span style="color:var(--sage);font-weight:600">$38,400 confirmed ARR</span>
    <span style="color:var(--muted);font-size:12px"> / $150,000 goal = </span>
    <span style="color:var(--sage);font-weight:700;font-size:16px">25.6%</span>
    <div style="background:var(--border);border-radius:20px;height:6px;margin-top:10px">
      <div style="background:var(--sage);width:25.6%;height:100%;border-radius:20px"></div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- CLIENT HEALTH -->
  <div class="section-title">👥 Client Health</div>

  <div class="client-card">
    <div class="client-header">
      <div>
        <div class="client-name">Dr. Wendy Ellis — VMC</div>
        <div class="client-biz">Veterinary Medical Center · lakewoodranchvet.com</div>
      </div>
      <span class="badge badge-green">LAUNCHED 🚀</span>
    </div>
    <div class="client-detail"><strong>Status:</strong> Site went live Friday, April 3. $2,000/mo retainer active. Colby Foundation site on hold (IT guy situation).</div>
    <div class="client-detail"><strong>Action:</strong> 2 email drafts unsent (Brooke rack cards + Wendy check-in). Send them today or Monday. Verify site live on multiple devices.</div>
    <div class="client-detail"><strong>Last contact:</strong> March 20 · <strong>Retainer:</strong> $2,000/mo</div>
  </div>

  <div class="client-card">
    <div class="client-header">
      <div>
        <div class="client-name">Clay Griffin — Hallwood Enterprises</div>
        <div class="client-biz">hallwood-usa.com · Virginia</div>
      </div>
      <span class="badge badge-warn">ACH INCOMING</span>
    </div>
    <div class="client-detail"><strong>Status:</strong> On retainer $600/mo via ACH on the 6th. Biweekly call Monday April 6 at 10 AM.</div>
    <div class="client-detail"><strong>Action:</strong> Verify Chase ACH cleared → mark HoneyBook invoice paid. Monday call: LinkedIn salesman changes + new contract questions.</div>
    <div class="client-detail"><strong>Last contact:</strong> April 2 · <strong>Retainer:</strong> $600/mo ACH</div>
  </div>

  <div class="client-card">
    <div class="client-header">
      <div>
        <div class="client-name">Derek Mardones — Busy Bee Movers</div>
        <div class="client-biz">movebusybee.com · Sarasota, FL</div>
      </div>
      <span class="badge badge-info">ONBOARDING</span>
    </div>
    <div class="client-detail"><strong>Status:</strong> New $600/mo Social Media Starter retainer. Start date April 1. Deposit ($300) still pending. Facebook admin access + ManyChat setup sent.</div>
    <div class="client-detail"><strong>Action:</strong> Text Derek to confirm: (1) Monday April 6 first photo session at 1 PM and (2) Tuesday call at 6 PM. Chase deposit if not received.</div>
    <div class="client-detail"><strong>Last contact:</strong> April 2 (Zoom) · <strong>Retainer:</strong> $600/mo · <strong>Deposit due:</strong> $300</div>
  </div>

  <div class="client-card">
    <div class="client-header">
      <div>
        <div class="client-name">Peleta Henderson — Jus' Poetic LLC</div>
        <div class="client-biz">juspoetic92@gmail.com</div>
      </div>
      <span class="badge badge-muted">WRAPPING UP</span>
    </div>
    <div class="client-detail"><strong>Status:</strong> Project nearly done. 8 revision items still pending. Friday April 3 at 1 PM call was scheduled re: $300/mo blog/SEO upsell.</div>
    <div class="client-detail"><strong>Action:</strong> Log Friday call outcome. Send warm follow-up. If she's interested — next step is contract + first blog post. If not — close warmly.</div>
    <div class="client-detail"><strong>Last contact:</strong> March 25 · <strong>Upsell potential:</strong> $300/mo blog retainer</div>
  </div>

  <hr class="divider">

  <!-- EMAIL ACTIVITY -->
  <div class="section-title">📬 Email Activity</div>
  <div class="card" style="margin-bottom:24px">
    <div class="email-row">
      <span class="email-icon">🔴</span>
      <div class="email-body">
        <div class="email-from">BOUNCED — Angela Jones <angela.jones013p@gmail.com></div>
        <div class="email-subj">"A Clothing" Logo Inquiry — $1K Budget</div>
        <div class="email-note">Sent to wrong address (angelajonesent@). RESEND to angela.jones013p@gmail.com — no links, all info in body.</div>
      </div>
      <span class="badge badge-danger">RESEND</span>
    </div>
    <div class="email-row">
      <span class="email-icon">🏦</span>
      <div class="email-body">
        <div class="email-from">Chase Bank — ACH Deposit Notification</div>
        <div class="email-subj">Likely Clay Griffin $600 Retainer (due 6th)</div>
        <div class="email-note">Check Chase and manually mark HoneyBook invoice paid if cleared.</div>
      </div>
      <span class="badge badge-warn">VERIFY</span>
    </div>
    <div class="email-row">
      <span class="email-icon">🌐</span>
      <div class="email-body">
        <div class="email-from">GoDaddy / Zoom — VMC Domain Transfer</div>
        <div class="email-subj">lakewoodranchvet.com post-launch domain setup</div>
        <div class="email-note">Confirm domain is pointing correctly and Zoom Phone integration is live for VMC.</div>
      </div>
      <span class="badge badge-green">REVIEW</span>
    </div>
    <div class="email-row">
      <span class="email-icon">🔄</span>
      <div class="email-body">
        <div class="email-from">Contra Pro — Subscription Renewal</div>
        <div class="email-subj">Renewing Monday April 6 — Decide to Keep or Cancel</div>
        <div class="email-note">Log in to Contra and cancel before Monday if not actively using it.</div>
      </div>
      <span class="badge badge-warn">DECIDE</span>
    </div>
    <div class="email-row">
      <span class="email-icon">📧</span>
      <div class="email-body">
        <div class="email-from">Kit (ConvertKit) — New Subscriber</div>
        <div class="email-subj">+1 subscriber to your email list</div>
        <div class="email-note">Growing slowly. Note who it is — may be a warm lead or past inquiry.</div>
      </div>
      <span class="badge badge-muted">FYI</span>
    </div>
    <div class="email-row">
      <span class="email-icon">📝</span>
      <div class="email-body">
        <div class="email-from">DRAFT — Brooke Kommuck (VMC)</div>
        <div class="email-subj">Rack Cards Resend + Website Check-in</div>
        <div class="email-note">Draft created Mar 17. Send now — post-VMC launch is the perfect moment to reconnect.</div>
      </div>
      <span class="badge badge-info">SEND</span>
    </div>
    <div class="email-row">
      <span class="email-icon">📝</span>
      <div class="email-body">
        <div class="email-from">DRAFT — Country Club Prospect</div>
        <div class="email-subj">Cold outreach draft waiting to be picked and sent</div>
        <div class="email-note">Pick one version and send it — this has been sitting. Takes 3 minutes.</div>
      </div>
      <span class="badge badge-info">SEND</span>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- WARM LEADS -->
  <div class="section-title">🔥 Warm Pipeline</div>
  <div class="grid-2" style="margin-bottom:24px">
    <div class="card">
      <div style="display:flex;justify-content:space-between;align-items:flex-start;margin-bottom:8px">
        <div>
          <div style="font-weight:600;color:var(--cream)">Nancy Pile-Griffin</div>
          <div style="color:var(--muted);font-size:11px">griffinzoo007@gmail.com · Clay's wife</div>
        </div>
        <span class="badge badge-danger">30 DAYS SILENT</span>
      </div>
      <div class="client-detail"><strong>Project:</strong> Trinity UMC logo redesign ($250) + possible peanut business logo</div>
      <div class="client-detail"><strong>Status:</strong> Nancy replied Feb 19 — Pastor Dan Kim wants to work with you directly. You haven't replied in nearly a month.</div>
      <div class="client-detail" style="color:#e07070"><strong>⚠️ $1,800 at risk</strong> — Clay is your biggest client. Ignoring his wife is a relationship risk.</div>
    </div>
    <div class="card">
      <div style="display:flex;justify-content:space-between;align-items:flex-start;margin-bottom:8px">
        <div>
          <div style="font-weight:600;color:var(--cream)">Angela Jones</div>
          <div style="color:var(--muted);font-size:11px">angela.jones013p@gmail.com</div>
        </div>
        <span class="badge badge-danger">BOUNCED</span>
      </div>
      <div class="client-detail"><strong>Project:</strong> "A Clothing" — minimal luxury logo, black/white/gold, $1K budget</div>
      <div class="client-detail"><strong>Status:</strong> Reply bounced April 2 (wrong address used). She won't click links — embed all info in email body.</div>
      <div class="client-detail"><strong>Action:</strong> Resend to angela.jones013p@gmail.com today. Don't let this cool off.</div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- VMC POST-LAUNCH CHECKLIST -->
  <div class="section-title">🏥 VMC Post-Launch Checklist</div>
  <div class="card" style="margin-bottom:24px">
    <p style="color:var(--muted);font-size:12px;margin-bottom:12px">Site launched Friday April 3. Critical items still pending:</p>
    <div class="checklist">
      <div class="check-row"><div class="check-dot dot-danger"></div><span>Community page — placeholder content needs to be replaced with real copy</span></div>
      <div class="check-row"><div class="check-dot dot-danger"></div><span>Surgery page — arthroscopy section has placeholder text ("Lorem ipsum" style)</span></div>
      <div class="check-row"><div class="check-dot dot-danger"></div><span>Radiology page — needs "UPDATE" text replaced with correct service description</span></div>
      <div class="check-row"><div class="check-dot dot-warn"></div><span>Contact form — potential bug reported, needs to be tested end-to-end</span></div>
      <div class="check-row"><div class="check-dot dot-warn"></div><span>Blog nav link — may not be displaying correctly in mobile nav</span></div>
      <div class="check-row"><div class="check-dot dot-ok"></div><span>Homepage hero — confirmed live and correct</span></div>
      <div class="check-row"><div class="check-dot dot-ok"></div><span>Rack cards (4x9 GotPrint) — previously resolved via PDF versions</span></div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- UPCOMING -->
  <div class="section-title">📅 Upcoming This Week</div>
  <div class="card" style="margin-bottom:24px">
    <div class="upcoming-list">
      <div class="upcoming-row">
        <div class="upcoming-day">Mon Apr 6</div>
        <div class="upcoming-desc"><strong style="color:var(--cream)">Clay Griffin biweekly call — 10:00 AM</strong> · LinkedIn salesman changes + new contract questions. Prep: review changes, have contract summary ready.</div>
      </div>
      <div class="upcoming-row">
        <div class="upcoming-day">Mon Apr 6</div>
        <div class="upcoming-desc"><strong style="color:var(--cream)">Derek Mardones — First Photo Session</strong> · 1st Monday afternoon. Confirm location/time. Bring shot list. This is the first deliverable of his $600/mo package.</div>
      </div>
      <div class="upcoming-row">
        <div class="upcoming-day">Mon Apr 6</div>
